other artiifacts

If the user is known and the user is smiling, the Lambda function sends a request to IOT
Core to dispense a piece of candy

object.label:

controller

demo.

object.label:
S3 is used for storing the single page HTML app used by the Display as well as all
images being shown. It is also used to store the single page HTML app used by the
mobile app. CloudFront is used as CDN in front of S3. Amazon Cognito Identity pool is
used to create temporary access tokens for getting access to AWS IOT Core from the
virtual candy dispenser and the admin mobile app
